\`\`\`

_Raise per-column statistics target:_
\`\`\`sql
ALTER TABLE users ALTER COLUMN <column> SET STATISTICS 1000;
ANALYZE users;
\`\`\`

_Add extended statistics for correlated columns:_
\`\`\`sql
